00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,730
You have entered the Real Estate section.

2
00:00:04,130 --> 00:00:06,530
While we continue to live in the real world,

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:12,380
many companies and individuals have begun to build their presence in the metaverse.

4
00:00:13,070 --> 00:00:19,460
Currently, the metaverse real estate market is as hot as a corner unit condo in Manhattan.

5
00:00:20,150 --> 00:00:27,860
You can even visit an office, shop at a store and clean your house in the virtual world these days.

6
00:00:28,490 --> 00:00:31,610
DECENTRALAND FOUNDATION, 2015

7
00:00:32,810 --> 00:00:36,590
A dilemma met by many NFT collectors was

8
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:40,550
”how do I display or even use my collection?”

9
00:00:41,420 --> 00:00:43,010
Enter Decentraland,

10
00:00:43,430 --> 00:00:50,930
a 3D virtual reality world where users can create their own avatar, buy land parcels,

11
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:56,060
interact with other users, attend concerts and exhibitions,

12
00:00:56,420 --> 00:00:59,630
build their own homes, and so much more.

13
00:01:00,410 --> 00:01:04,430
Users are beginning to form communities in Decentraland,

14
00:01:04,670 --> 00:01:10,040
which are growing all the time in this ever-evolving virtual world.

15
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:17,490
Each land parcel in Decentraland is an NFT and is unique to its own plot.

16
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:26,220
On these plots of land, users can build their own spaces and exhibit their wider NFT collections.

17
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:32,940
Over the last year several corporations have started to build their own presence in the metaverse.

18
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:38,870
Sotheby’s built a virtual replica of their new Bond Street location in Decentraland

19
00:01:39,050 --> 00:01:44,090
and more recently, the real estate investment company Republic Realm

20
00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:53,360
purchased 259 land parcels on which it will build a virtual shopping district called Metajuku,

21
00:01:53,810 --> 00:01:56,510
named after Tokyo’s Harajuku.

22
00:01:57,450 --> 00:02:03,480
Decentraland is one of the fastest growing real estate marketplaces for the metaverse.

